title: Siege of the Dwarven Dam: Greenskin Invasion - Total War: WARHAMMER Gameplay
description:
Siege of the Dwarven Dam: Greenskin Invasion - Total War: WARHAMMER Gameplay - A Massive army of Greenskins invade a strategic Dwarven Dam.  The Dwarves rallied as many troops as possible to make their last stand!  This is a 3v3 Online battle on Total War: Warhammer.  There are only 2 factions on the battlefield Dwarfs and GreenSkins!  Enjoy the Battle :D

Map: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=925850029&searchtext=dwarvendam

Longer Battles Mod: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=834648466

Discord Link: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
